headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of Netflix (NFLX)
summary: Since April 2025, Netflix has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 2.2% while floating around $1,101. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 23.9% gain during that period.
